headline.main: R.A.F. FLIERS BLAST FOE'S LIBYAN BASES; Bardia an Objective -- Italians' Garrison There Displaying 'No Sign of Activity' POSTS IN ERITREA BOMBED Rome Reports Aerial Assaults Against the British Forces on North African Front

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Jan. 2 (UP) -- Smashing British bombing raids on Italian objectives in Africa, including besieged Bardia, were reported today by the Royal Air Force Command.
abstract: RAF repts raids on Ital Libyan bases
